20:
No child will die when it is still an infant;
\q2 all people will live until they are very old.
\q1 People will consider that anyone who is a hundred years old is still young;
\q2 they will consider that anyone who dies who is younger than that has been cursed.
\q1

24:
Before they call to me to help them, I will answer;
\q2 I will answer their prayers while they are still praying for me to do something for them.
\q1
